      "text": [
        "۳۹۸. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): ضَعْ فَخْرَكَ، وَاحْطُطْ كِبْرَكَ، وَاذْكُرْ قَبْرَكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "398. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Put off boasting, give up self-conceit and remember your grave."
        ]
